profile: Sweeney Eye Associates is an Ophthalmology practice dedicated to providing the highest quality eye care services that our patients deserve. Although we specialize in cataract surgery, we offer comprehensive vision correction and eye care treatment using the most advanced diagnostic and surgical technology. Our Physicians and Optometrist are highly experienced and specialty trained to treat cataracts, glaucoma, diabetic, and retina disease along with general eye care. We offer a selection of advanced technology and lifestyle changing intraocular lens implants for vision correction and provide a state of the art surgical center conveniently located next to our clinic.
